================================================================================
The portal — Next.js front-end (analog-elk-front-end)
================================================================================

The Elk OS portal image is built from a pinned commit of analog-elk-front-end
(Analog Elk's own application, vendored read-only at build time; see
portal/PINNED_COMMIT and portal/.build/ATTRIBUTION.md). It carries its own
attribution for the same Agency OS lineage and its bundled open-source
dependencies.

